Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,(公元2096年8月16日)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 明天就要去冲绳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.41,0:00:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在烦恼要带哪套衣服过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥您准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也还没
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,休假前要处理的工作太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该开始准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我收拾好这里之后也去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,餐后清理是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是水波 你也要忙着辅助哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 属下昨晚就准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪大人不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请去做好旅行的准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:00:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给属下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,距离那时候已经4年了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,(魔法科高中的劣等生 追忆篇)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,(公元2092年8月4日 冲绳上空)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位旅客
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本班机10分后抵达那霸机场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请确实系好安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,整理好您的随身物品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,(冲绳 那霸机场)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,(欢迎来到那霸)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅长面对这位哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为达也是你的“守护者”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是哥哥也等同于佣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你是他的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那请不要盯着我看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恕在下失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然不擅长面对这位哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也欢迎深雪与达也一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,穗波小姐您好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要受您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麦茶已经冰好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要泡热茶给您?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得冰好了 我喝麦茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是 遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪与达也也要喝麦茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,劳烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲大人 我出去走走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你擦一下防晒乳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冲绳的阳光比本土强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来仔细帮你擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己来就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,穗波小姐 您要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须好好防护才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前面…胸部我自己擦就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那这里由我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,腿我也可以自己擦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,裙子底下应该不需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么母亲大人 我去散步一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 带达也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服的风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要带着守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是散步 明明不需要护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,何况哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人不是比我弱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正派不上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明用不着担任我的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要被那个人保护
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我解除那个人的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人就能自由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使不再是我的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人也不一定能自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果只是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也没理由要他继续当我的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么要留住那个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明不擅长面对那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明不喜欢那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 很痛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你走路看哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是“遗族血统”的第二代?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前驻日美军第二代大多品行不良
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,观光导览都会提醒游客注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不想和小鬼打交道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到发不出声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没种的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,耍什么帅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我有CAD
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会放任他们乱骂人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不打算要求道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你们请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样对彼此都好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定有听到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我跪地磕头求饶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看在你胆子够大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就饶你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是用了魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 刚才没有这种征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本只是想捉弄一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你接下来会吃不完兜著走喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要说得这么挑衅?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对打不赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,区区小鬼 口气还满大的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人原来那么强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才被陌生男人找麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更正 哥哥保护我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也 你立了大功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是在下的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,认清自己的立场是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也 今后也继续努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我去冲个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,“使命”是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是立场?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人之所以保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是基于守护者的义务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么在哭?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么一定要掉眼泪?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 我是穗波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来已经打扮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,穗波小姐 母亲大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人正在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是稍微发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天应该就会康复
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我想陪着母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是应该不能如愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚的邀请人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是四叶分家之一 黑羽家的当家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说也是很重要的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟只有我能代替母亲大人出席
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这份心态很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但你表情这么抗拒 会糟蹋了这身打扮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看得出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是我才看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 请不要捉弄我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过世上很多人的“眼光”比我好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一眼就能看出你在抗拒的这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许就在今晚宴会的来宾之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么说可能有点严格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过有损你自身评价的举止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须趁现在尽早改善
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问我该怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重点是巧妙瞒骗自己的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的表面工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须先让自己能接受才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果穗波小姐也能一起来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是有达也陪着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说那个人陪着…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 和黑羽舅父打交道的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实要由身为长子的他负责吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别露出这种表情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原本明明会是感情很好的兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也不是我这种“调整体”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是人工打造的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不需要成为守护者才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是不认为他们两位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的关系是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,舅父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您今天的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你来 深雪小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,令堂还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙您这么关心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,家母应该只是有点疲累
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天还是请她以身体为重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听你这么说 我也放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别站在这里说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亚夜子与文弥也很期待见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亚夜子 文弥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两位过得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来姐姐您也没变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,文弥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿这样不会热吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也是黑羽家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须随时穿得体面才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得知美丽的姐姐您要来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也精心盛装打扮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好强烈的竞争心态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也哥哥没和您一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人在那里待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了 真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然让重要的来宾落单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人笑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嘲笑 也不是苦笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是自然而然的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不曾对我露出那种笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,文弥 亚夜子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以打扰达也工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你确实尽到了本分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:28.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微聊一下没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做好防范措施保护来宾的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是我们主办人的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑羽家的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有无能到无法保证每位宾客的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您说对吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,舅父大人肯定是想这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望自己的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是文弥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要对那个人示好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,文弥是四叶家下任当家候选人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样是候选人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他却崇拜我身旁的平凡护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是很丢脸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是佣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是用完就扔的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身为“四叶”理所当然要这么看待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了成为“四叶深雪”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须保持相同的心态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人不只是哥哥 更是守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身为道具的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不会对我怀抱亲情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不该对那个人怀抱情感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥是我的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是保护我的盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,文弥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以过度害令尊为难喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我这时露出不悦表情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会被误解我不满舅父大人与哥哥的对应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是误解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以想这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的表面工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须先让自己能接受才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑羽先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会场内部方便麻烦您看管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在下到外面巡视一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心态可嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪小妹的安全就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连好好聊一聊都不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也先生 请早点回来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 我巡视一圈就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥在忠实执行自己的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要努力扮演好自己的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,(公元2092年8月5日)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来由我拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请穗波小姐坐在母亲大人旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,穗波 偶尔一次没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然夫人这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,穗波小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请再靠近母亲大人一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,穗波小姐 您的笑容很棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来换你和达也合照吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两位也要偶尔拍一次合照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也觉得怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:21:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人 您意下如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然夫人也允许了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也 请坐在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦笑一个喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,疑似是潜舰的船影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正从船尾方向接近本船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,潜舰侵犯领海?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是企图发动战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人 请进船舱避难
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 麻烦陪在夫人身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来支援
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连CAD都不带
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么不擅长魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好歹也是魔法师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼雷?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是想做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.26,0:23:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是…魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明没有CAD
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.64,0:23:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么做到的?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人其实会使用魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是那么高阶的魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平常都假装不会使用魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来我对这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一无所知?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,(公元2092年8月5日)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 本官再确认一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说游艇被潜舰的鱼雷攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于遇袭的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:23:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问各位心里有底吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.57,0:24:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们完全想不到原因
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.11,0:24:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.20,0:24:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多就问到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.20,0:24:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该无法提供帮得上忙的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.42,0:24:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.21,0:24:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢各位的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.85,0:24:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.35,0:24:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先前打倒乔的少年是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.31,0:24:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,年纪轻轻就习得“透劲”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.19,0:24:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的天分值得惊叹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.78,0:24:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桧垣上兵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.04,0:24:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,部下在昨天有所冒犯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.83,0:24:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,容本官谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.00,0:25:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是上兵桧垣乔瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.84,0:25:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天非常失礼 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.26,0:25:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.64,0:25:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.15,0:25:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫做司波达也吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.48,0:25:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本官正在恩纳基地
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.82,0:25:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兼任空降魔法师部队的教官
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.86,0:25:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有空的话 务必来基地看看
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.03,0:25:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里肯定能让你感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.37,0:25:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.88,0:25:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出车
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.14,0:25:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,(公元2092年8月6日)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.62,0:26:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人今天要安排什么行程?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.17,0:26:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种天气逛街购物也不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.01,0:26:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么安排呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.63,0:26:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,属下想想
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.14,0:26:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要去欣赏琉球舞蹈?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.85,0:26:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说也可以换上舞蹈服体验
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.44,0:26:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.27,0:26:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 你觉得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.36,0:26:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我也觉得很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.37,0:27:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那属下去安排车子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.41,0:27:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那个活动好像只限女性参加
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.17,0:27:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.58,0:27:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.96,0:27:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.30,0:27:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记得昨天那位上尉邀你去基地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.22,0:27:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个好机会 你去观摩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.51,0:27:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或许可以获准参与训练
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.27,0:27:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.94,0:27:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.36,0:27:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问我…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.78,0:27:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以和哥哥一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.49,0:27:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.33,0:27:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.58,0:27:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也对军方魔法师的训练感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.96,0:27:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且身为主人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.29,0:27:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也必须掌握自己守护者的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.38,0:27:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 你的心态可嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.84,0:28:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但你们目前表面上是兄妹关系
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.27,0:28:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也 如你刚才听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.98,0:28:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪会一起去参观基地
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.48,0:28:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.65,0:28:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的外出行程
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.11,0:28:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须表现成兄妹的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.57,0:28:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能称呼深雪是“大小姐”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.20,0:28:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要叫她“深雪”
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.78,0:28:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也要避免使用敬语
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.58,0:28:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.87,0:28:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪也没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.66,0:28:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.39,0:28:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是陆军兵器开发部的真田
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.02,0:28:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是司波达也
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.65,0:28:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.07,0:28:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是妹妹司波深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.99,0:29:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.49,0:29:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两位客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.91,0:29:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你们前来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.99,0:29:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.60,0:29:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到恩纳基地
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.19,0:29:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就来观摩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.90,0:29:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以解释为你对军方有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.02,0:29:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.78,0:29:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但我没决定要不要从军
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.95,0:29:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.03,0:29:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记得你还是国中生?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.49,0:29:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚升上国中
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.00,0:29:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的个性很稳重
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.41,0:29:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.92,0:29:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问各位都是魔法师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.59,0:29:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.50,0:30:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在战场上可能会无法使用CAD
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.30,0:30:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以作战行动需要的最底限魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.93,0:30:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须训练自己能够徒手发动
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.69,0:30:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再来是闯关形式的对打
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.53,0:30:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一的规定是必须赤手空拳
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.53,0:30:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一对一
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.65,0:30:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到打输才停止
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.91,0:30:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.50,0:30:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,司波 光是旁观很无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.75,0:30:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要加入挑战?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.26,0:30:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.80,0:30:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,机会难得 所以麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.14,0:30:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,渡久地中士
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.89,0:30:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.14,0:30:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你来陪司波过几招
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.18,0:30:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.81,0:30:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,司波 不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.36,0:30:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,渡久地中士是在学生时代
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.44,0:31:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打进国民体育拳击赛的实力派
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.62,0:31:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请赐教
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.79,0:31:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手下留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.85,0:31:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.35,0:31:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,南风原下士
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.94,0:31:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.77,0:31:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准放水
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.36,0:31:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.56,0:31:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.75,0:31:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是实战型
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.67,0:31:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他看出南风原下士精通兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.88,0:32:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是冲绳空手道高手
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.92,0:32:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,闪躲的时候刻意躲远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.09,0:32:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是预测对方可能暗藏武器
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.72,0:32:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.53,0:32:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.82,0:32:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你的本事这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.74,0:32:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.04,0:32:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.79,0:32:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恩纳空降部队将会颜面扫地
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.80,0:32:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以请你再打一场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.55,0:32:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以擅自决定…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.43,0:32:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请让在下上场
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.93,0:32:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桧垣上兵
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.56,0:32:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想报复
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.93,0:32:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本官不会答应
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.06,0:33:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是报复
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.60,0:33:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是雪耻
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.86,0:33:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,司波 他自己这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.40,0:33:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意奉陪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.90,0:33:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桧垣上兵很年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.45,0:33:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却是不输南风原的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.32,0:33:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,容我讨教
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.91,0:33:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.29,0:33:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.61,0:33:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.90,0:33:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不卑鄙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.91,0:33:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了 深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.53,0:33:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法师在实战使用魔法是理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.12,0:34:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚才叫我“深雪”…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.94,0:34:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是“术式解体”
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.94,0:34:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.19,0:34:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全败北
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.12,0:34:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在彻底明白前天打输你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.79,0:34:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.41,0:34:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,容我再度自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.42,0:34:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是国防陆军恩纳空降部队
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.96,0:34:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桧垣乔瑟夫上兵
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.30,0:34:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是司波达也
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.39,0:34:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 达也
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.30,0:35:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以后叫我乔就好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.68,0:35:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还会在冲绳待一阵子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.23,0:35:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊的话来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.65,0:35:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样 我在附近很吃得开
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.23,0:35:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止 乔
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.65,0:35:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还在训练
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.61,0:35:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉刚才提出无理的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.62,0:35:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来部下心底的芥蒂也消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.95,0:35:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,方便一起喝杯茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.62,0:35:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于刚才的“发劲”
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.67,0:35:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 本官也想请教一下
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.71,0:35:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也请务必看看我正在开发的CAD
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.01,0:35:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不理你了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.07,0:35:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,(公元2092年8月11日)
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.00,0:36:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从早上就一直做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.42,0:36:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会腻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.88,0:36:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.42,0:36:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃午饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.64,0:36:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.69,0:36:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.94,0:36:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.25,0:36:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,国防军发布紧急警报
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.71,0:36:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在渡名喜岛东方十公里处海域
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.88,0:36:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,航行中的我国海防艇
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.09,0:36:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被国籍不明的潜舰攻击而失联
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.46,0:36:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我军立刻紧急出动
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.38,0:36:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是尚未逮捕或击沉敌方潜舰
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.34,0:37:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,庆良间群岛被海中发射的导弹攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.85,0:37:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,港湾设施受到损害
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.60,0:37:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,收看本频道的各位观众
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.10,0:37:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请依照紧急事态应变指南
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.27,0:37:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迅速并且冷静开始避难
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.53,0:37:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一次 国防军发布…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.78,0:37:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.61,0:37:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恩纳基地的风间上尉打电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.87,0:37:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请我们去基地的避难所避难
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.51,0:37:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.51,0:37:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 属下知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.68,0:37:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.68,0:37:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真夜大人打电话给您
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.57,0:37:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 真夜?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.19,0:38:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.82,0:38:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你那边发生大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.33,0:38:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.83,0:38:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风间上尉连络你们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.83,0:38:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,基地避难所那件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.17,0:38:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你安排的 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.46,0:38:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过基地是敌军的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.63,0:38:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样反而危险吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.80,0:38:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,军事以外的设施也会被攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.06,0:38:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟对方不会遵守公约
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.10,0:38:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们总是不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.31,0:38:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐肯定也很清楚这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.40,0:38:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也对 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.07,0:38:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐这么明理 我松了口气
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.86,0:38:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,方便我再提供一个建议吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.91,0:38:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 请说
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.58,0:38:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是这种状况
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.54,0:38:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为最好将达也“解放”
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.58,0:38:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是认真这么说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.25,0:39:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是可以暂时解除他的限制
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.72,0:39:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以姐姐的能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.88,0:39:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连碰都不碰就能自由解除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.55,0:39:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.60,0:39:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在意这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.18,0:39:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这么做比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.73,0:39:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是四叶家当家的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.82,0:39:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么姐姐 请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.53,0:39:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.83,0:39:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人 真夜大人怎么说?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.20,0:39:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,国防军的避难所会收容我们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.21,0:39:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经预先知会了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.25,0:39:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 打给达也的电话是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.25,0:39:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.92,0:39:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.17,0:39:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.26,0:39:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通知上尉说我们接受邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.35,0:39:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后请他派人来接我们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.31,0:39:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.07,0:40:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在下是桧垣上兵
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.58,0:40:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先带各位前往二楼的休息室
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.50,0:40:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,避难所准备好就会带各位过去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.13,0:40:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请在这里稍待片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.85,0:40:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人 您不觉得奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.44,0:40:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说避难所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.23,0:40:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.32,0:40:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,避难所要能紧急避难才有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.36,0:40:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,需要进行什么准备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.66,0:40:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.37,0:41:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是需要花时间掩饰高官们抢著逃走的事实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.46,0:41:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有事的 深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.38,0:41:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.76,0:41:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,“深雪”?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.30,0:41:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人…哥哥又叫我“深雪”了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.60,0:41:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然这么乱说话
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.56,0:41:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,“我陪着你 所以不会有事”是怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.48,0:41:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你凭什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.52,0:41:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这样…犯规了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.57,0:41:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也 刚才那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.62,0:41:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是枪声
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.67,0:41:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道状况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.46,0:41:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 从这里没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.64,0:41:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个房间有妨碍魔法的某种机关
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.68,0:42:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过并非无法使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.56,0:42:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也 你出去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.94,0:42:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是既然不清楚现状
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.69,0:42:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法忽视在这里受害的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.57,0:42:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,万一敌人入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.78,0:42:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将无法保护深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.12,0:42:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直呼“深雪”?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.03,0:42:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也 认清自己的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.04,0:42:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恕在下失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.80,0:42:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给穗波就好
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.72,0:42:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.06,0:42:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井小姐 这里拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.19,0:42:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.06,0:42:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也你也要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.50,0:43:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.26,0:43:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是空降第二中队的金城一兵
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.85,0:43:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,负责带各位前往地下避难所
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.56,0:43:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.98,0:43:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.19,0:43:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有一个人去外面观察状况
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.11,0:43:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过部分敌人已经入侵基地
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.07,0:43:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待在这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.61,0:43:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请先带那边的人们过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.37,0:43:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.04,0:43:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫做金城是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.41,0:43:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她们都已经那么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.04,0:43:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少先带我们过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.09,0:43:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人 您如果担心达也
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.38,0:43:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要拜托风间上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.18,0:43:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他要和我们会合应该不难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.76,0:44:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是在担心达也
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.93,0:44:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是表面上的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.02,0:44:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.85,0:44:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不能相信他们
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.61,0:44:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.09,0:44:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.63,0:44:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迪克 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.63,0:44:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,马克 班
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.09,0:44:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.84,0:44:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么背叛军队?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.85,0:44:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乔
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.76,0:44:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才想问你为什么要效忠日本?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.93,0:44:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了吗 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.52,0:44:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本不是我们的祖国吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.77,0:44:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本是怎么对待我们的?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.57,0:44:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算像这样志愿从军 为日本效力
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.45,0:45:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到头来还是“遗族血统”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.45,0:45:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,经过再久依然被当成外人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.62,0:45:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的误解
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.91,0:45:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在军中 在部队
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.83,0:45:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都把我们当成战友对待
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.58,0:45:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都把我们视为同伴接纳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.80,0:45:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乔 那是因为你是魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.18,0:45:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你具备魔法师的利用价值
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.80,0:45:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,军方才会给你好脸色
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.47,0:45:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迪克 你居然说这种话?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.02,0:45:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你很气别人拿“遗族血统”来排挤你
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.32,0:45:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却因为我是魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.23,0:45:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就又说我和你们不一样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.53,0:45:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不把我当成同伴吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.45,0:45:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.87,0:45:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乔
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.21,0:45:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.14,0:46:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,精神冻结魔法“悲叹冥河”
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.35,0:46:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,马克
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.52,0:46:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的魔法师!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.68,0:46:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.35,0:46:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.98,0:46:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.19,0:47:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你死
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.74,0:47:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.96,0:47:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.33,0:47:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点 深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.38,0:47:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音是哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.13,0:47:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥舍不得我死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.10,0:47:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明总是对你那么过分
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.18,0:47:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.39,0:47:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,-死掉之前 -深雪…深雪!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.31,0:47:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想至少向你说声对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.03,0:47:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.11,0:47:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身体使不上力
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.90,0:48:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我逐渐被填满
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.44,0:48:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我逐渐被重新打造
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.37,0:48:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.46,0:48:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.64,0:48:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是了不起的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.60,0:48:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太了不起了 我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.32,0:49:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.32,0:49:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.94,0:49:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.03,0:49:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伤逐渐痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.33,0:49:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连衣服的弹孔也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.41,0:49:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.77,0:50:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才不是中枪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.06,0:50:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是多亏了哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.19,0:50:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏达也?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.81,0:50:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,治疗魔法应该治不好这么重的伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.73,0:50:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥他做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.53,0:50:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 他是我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.71,0:50:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.67,0:50:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次内部出现叛军
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.09,0:50:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全是这边的疏失
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.76,0:50:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然做任何事都无法赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.84,0:50:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们国防军
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.09,0:50:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会尽量在各方面给个方便
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.10,0:50:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先麻烦说明正确的现状
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.85,0:51:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叛军的目标是那一家人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.48,0:51:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.56,0:51:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那名男性是军方重要客户的社长
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.77,0:51:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叛军好像想抓他当人质
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.07,0:51:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们是被波及的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.41,0:51:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这部分我们也不知道该如何道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.28,0:51:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 知道对方的目标不是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.00,0:51:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在下就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.83,0:51:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以侵略与迎击状况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.38,0:51:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌军多数登陆艇正接近恩纳村海岸
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.96,0:51:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,庆良间群岛近海
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.51,0:51:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,则被敌方掌握了制海权
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.18,0:51:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从那霸到名护
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.72,0:51:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和敌方串通的游击兵
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.93,0:51:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在各处妨碍我军兵力调度
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.98,0:51:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,游击兵已经收拾八成左右
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.06,0:51:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于敌方的抢滩部队
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.98,0:51:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本基地的空降部队即将出动
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.36,0:51:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在下理解状况了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.53,0:51:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.99,0:51:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请将家母 妹妹与樱井小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.99,0:52:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,收容在最安全的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.08,0:52:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,收容在防空司令室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.12,0:52:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.83,0:52:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么在最后
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.16,0:52:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请借在下装甲服与一套步兵装备
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.50,0:52:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.96,0:52:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们对深雪出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.67,0:52:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须让他们接受报应
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.76,0:52:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要一个人去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.35,0:52:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在下要做的是私人报复
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.44,0:52:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是抱持复仇心态上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.94,0:52:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能控制情绪就不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.57,0:52:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但本官不能允许你屠杀非战斗人员或投降士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.07,0:52:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在下不会让他们有时间投降
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.66,0:52:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.95,0:52:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这次的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.08,0:52:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原本就是击退
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.45,0:52:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或歼灭侵略军
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.79,0:52:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也没必要劝对方投降
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.71,0:52:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,司波达也 加入我们的战斗行列吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.21,0:52:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在下不打算听从军方指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.92,0:52:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在下要保护的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.88,0:53:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和各位要保护的事物不同
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.55,0:53:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 既然目的一样是歼灭敌军
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.64,0:53:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就一起并肩作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.27,0:53:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真田 借他装甲服与近战装备
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.61,0:53:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,空降部队十分钟后出击
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.15,0:53:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.15,0:53:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,司波 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.87,0:53:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井小姐 母亲与妹妹麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.09,0:53:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.64,0:53:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.64,0:53:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请您不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.31,0:53:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说 上战场也太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.19,0:54:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥您根本不必冒这种险
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.07,0:54:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在外面等你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.20,0:54:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实没这个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.00,0:54:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我自己的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.00,0:54:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会放过伤害你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.17,0:54:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会除掉所有危害你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.92,0:54:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.18,0:54:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我无法善罢甘休
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.72,0:54:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 我真正能够重视的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.81,0:54:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 只有你一人
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.77,0:54:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能够重视的事物?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.61,0:54:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.11,0:54:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你差不多也可以知道真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.57,0:54:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不必知道
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.91,0:54:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很希望你永远不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.50,0:54:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.41,0:54:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这件事也不该由我告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.08,0:54:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.34,0:54:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请母亲大人告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.67,0:55:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在的疑问都会得到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.43,0:55:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问母亲大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.26,0:55:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.80,0:55:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真正能够重视的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.89,0:55:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有深雪你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.27,0:55:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我今后也会继续保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.48,0:55:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且为此平安回到你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.57,0:55:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.78,0:55:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何人能真正令我受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.30,0:55:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 夫人醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.63,0:55:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.06,0:55:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,空降部队即将抵达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.02,0:56:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌方5艘登陆舰正接近海岸线
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.78,0:56:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于敌军来说应该是恶梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.91,0:56:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种程度是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.58,0:56:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲大人 我想请教一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.79,0:57:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥刚才说
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.67,0:57:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他真正能够重视的事物只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.34,0:57:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不是“重要的事物”
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.93,0:57:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是“能够重视的事物”
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.34,0:57:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我询问哥哥原因
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.31,0:57:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥要我请教母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.43,0:57:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 达也这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.40,0:57:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多可以告诉你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.86,0:57:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在这之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.73,0:57:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于达也那种不成材的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.03,0:57:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不准这么尊敬地称他“哥哥”
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.62,0:57:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.49,0:57:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥以他的能力救了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.62,0:57:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说刚才那件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.62,0:57:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子只有那个能力
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.21,0:57:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那个能力?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.21,0:57:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.59,0:57:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依照魔法师的标准
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.80,0:57:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也一出生就是个瑕疵品
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.76,0:57:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法是改写情报体与事象的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.02,0:57:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是达也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.52,0:58:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.02,0:58:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有分解情报体
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.40,0:58:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与重组情报体
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.53,0:58:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法是让情报体产生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.90,0:58:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子天生没有这种魔法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.37,0:58:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以魔法师来说无疑是瑕疵品
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.33,0:58:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他的重组能力救了我们一命
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.04,0:58:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那个能力严格来说不是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.76,0:58:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 哥哥的那种能力是?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.39,0:58:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不叫做魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.10,0:58:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要叫做“奇迹”吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.02,0:58:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们四叶是冠名“十师族”的魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.14,0:58:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有魔法师能成为四叶家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.86,0:58:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法使用魔法的那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.61,0:58:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没资格在四叶家活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.78,0:58:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.49,0:58:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我与真夜在七年前
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.20,0:58:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,决定为那孩子进行某项手术
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.20,0:59:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,“人造魔法师计划”
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.62,0:59:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在非魔法师的人的意识领域中
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.63,0:59:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,植入人工魔法演算领域
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.67,0:59:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是一项赋予魔法师能力的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.68,0:59:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,进行这项精神改造手术之后
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.59,0:59:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子的情感出现缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.52,0:59:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 与其说是“情感”
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.68,0:59:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说“情绪波动”比较合适
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.73,0:59:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,强烈的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.86,0:59:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深沉的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.27,0:59:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,激烈的嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.69,0:59:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怨恨 憎恶
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.48,0:59:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过度的食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.90,0:59:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过当的性欲
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.53,0:59:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盲目的恋爱情感
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.07,0:59:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会令人“忘我”的情绪波动
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.08,0:59:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也除了“唯一的例外”全部丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.87,0:59:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因而得到操控魔法的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.75,0:59:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.84,0:59:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说来遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.51,0:59:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人工魔法演算领域的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.22,1:00:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,远不如先天的魔法演算领域
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.14,1:00:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果他只能当成“守护者”来使用
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.02,1:00:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这项手术是母亲大人进行的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.90,1:00:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我做得到吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.83,1:00:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我察觉了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.37,1:00:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被这个实验夺走部分情感的人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.62,1:00:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是只有哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.63,1:00:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先不提手术的事
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.01,1:00:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也为何不把你视为“重要的事物”
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.43,1:00:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是视为“能够重视的事物”
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.26,1:00:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来回答这个疑问吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.93,1:00:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我不想听
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.56,1:00:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也没丧失的“唯一例外”就是答案
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.23,1:00:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.02,1:00:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他仅存唯一的情绪波动是兄妹之情
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.44,1:00:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是深爱你这个妹妹
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.24,1:01:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要保护你的情感
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.78,1:01:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别再说了 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.37,1:01:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他仅存唯一的真正情感
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.21,1:01:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也很清楚自己的状况
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.34,1:01:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他说的“能够重视”就是这个意思吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.63,1:01:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他只把我认知为“母亲”
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.72,1:01:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有理应附带的母子之情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.39,1:01:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲大人是刻意选择这个结果吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.94,1:01:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然只能留下一种情绪波动
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.15,1:01:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为应该留下他对你的情感
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.37,1:01:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我该如何报答哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.91,1:01:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该拿什么东西回报哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.25,1:01:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我明明连这条生命
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.34,1:01:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是从哥哥那里获得的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.76,1:02:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还想问什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.80,1:02:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.47,1:02:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.61,1:02:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,推测是敌军机动舰队的舰影
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.24,1:02:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正在从粟国岛北方接近
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.87,1:02:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.37,1:02:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,舰队编成是高速巡洋舰2
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.83,1:02:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,驱逐舰4
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.25,1:02:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本基地20分钟后
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.58,1:02:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,进入敌方射程范围
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.75,1:02:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,援军还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.04,1:02:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新田原出动4支飞行小队
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.55,1:02:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,约20分钟后抵达
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.76,1:02:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,勉强赶得上吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.38,1:02:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌舰迎击得怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.68,1:02:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在庆良间群岛海域
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.01,1:02:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我军防卫队正在交战
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.97,1:02:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海军在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.77,1:02:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,命令正在和敌军登陆部队交战的空降部队撤退
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.24,1:03:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,战况看来不甚理想
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.58,1:03:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能射得中的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.83,1:03:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底想做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.30,1:03:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.05,1:03:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人 属下有事相求
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.97,1:03:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.43,1:03:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,属下想去迎接达也
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.73,1:03:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,穗波 你是我的护卫吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.73,1:03:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.78,1:03:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.70,1:03:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 你去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.36,1:03:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来达也想使用“那个”
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.95,1:03:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就去协助他吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.45,1:03:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢夫人
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.96,1:03:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问您说的“那个”是?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.50,1:04:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是知道理论上做得到
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.30,1:04:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上肯定没尝试过
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.34,1:04:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那孩子大概有什么想法吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.10,1:04:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两位请回基地
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.47,1:04:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给在下就够了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.06,1:04:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准说傻话
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.52,1:04:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要一起回去
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.81,1:04:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恕难从命
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.44,1:04:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须歼灭敌方舰队
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.40,1:04:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,否则基地有危险
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.57,1:04:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了你的家人吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.45,1:04:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么至少应该换个地点
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.57,1:04:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.45,1:04:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在来不及寻找别的射击位置
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.21,1:04:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们也留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.42,1:04:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在下失败的话
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.17,1:04:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将会殃及两位
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.67,1:04:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何作战可以百分百成功
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.05,1:04:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有任何战场毫无战死的危险
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.85,1:04:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若胜败乃兵家常事
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.10,1:04:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生死即为兵士常事
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.11,1:05:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真田 由我们来防守
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.61,1:05:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.57,1:05:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,司波专心准备攻击舰队的魔法
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.90,1:05:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这下子快招架不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.86,1:05:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不准说丧气话
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.11,1:05:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 虽然您这么说
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.57,1:05:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但下官的魔法本来就缺乏速度
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.62,1:05:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,计算子弹落入敌方舰队中央的轨道
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.02,1:06:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来协助
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.15,1:06:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,护盾强度居然匹敌十文字家?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.32,1:06:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是勉强使用这种魔法
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.87,1:06:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她的身体撑得住吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.08,1:06:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,轨道计算完毕
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.01,1:06:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,“质量爆散” 发动
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.60,1:07:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已完全剥夺敌方舰队战力
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.31,1:07:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达也 辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.07,1:07:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,穗波小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.90,1:07:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是海啸
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.55,1:07:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 达也
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.52,1:07:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是既定的寿命
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.06,1:07:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.77,1:07:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.19,1:07:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是“调整体”
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.52,1:07:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候耗尽生命都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.49,1:07:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我出生之前就负起护盾的职责
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.53,1:08:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在今天完成并结束这项职责
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.37,1:08:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是受到任何人的指使
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.92,1:08:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是以自己的意愿完成了职责
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.21,1:08:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么做
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.84,1:08:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今毫无选择生存方式的自由
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.56,1:08:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却得以自己选择葬身之所
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.10,1:08:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不打算放过这个机会
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.35,1:08:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是以人造道具的身份
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.02,1:08:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是能以人类的身份死去
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.78,1:08:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就这么让我死吧
